  "title": "Healthier SG app ambassador (1 year contract) #HKH",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Conduct appointment reminders to patients on their upcoming appointment or assist patient in scheduling their next appointment</li><li>Participate in outreach activities, including sending of SMSes, making phone calls, and distributing mailers, to patients who are yet enrolled in HSG</li><li>Coordinate and book HSG consultation appointments for enrolled patients</li><li>Communicating of “My Care Team” to patients</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Min N / O / A / Diploma in any courses</li><li>Able to start work immediately</li></ul><p><strong>Mon to Fri, office hours</strong></p><p>Interested candidates please send a copy of your resume in MS Word to kevynhuang@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p><br /></p><p>Consultant: Huang Jingsheng Kevyn (R1333338)</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd (99C4599)</p>",
